生物的关系是什么？ [#Raden 老师和 Pinolabo/Yukurasuutei Raden/Carlo Pino]" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/O6uORheNkfQ?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>此外， <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@raden_gakuya" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Yūkarasubutei Raden</strong></a>和<a href="https://www.youtube.com/@ShiorihaRuri" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Ruri Shioriha</strong></a>等VTuber也出现了，他们热情地介绍看似困难的话题，并得到了观众的积极反馈，称他们让学习变得有趣。</p><p>这次，我们将从知识型和学术型的VTuber中挑选一些正在进行有趣活动的VTuber，并按类型进行介绍。</p><h2>民俗/诸星</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/159a9b31b861bcde780a6cbbfed13517-kix.iannqikdcwak-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/159a9b31b861bcde780a6cbbfed13517-kix.iannqikdcwak-1024x571.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/159a9b31b861bcde780a6cbbfed13517-kix.iannqikdcwak-1024x571.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/159a9b31b861bcde780a6cbbfed13517-kix.iannqikdcwak-300x167.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/159a9b31b861bcde780a6cbbfed13517-kix.iannqikdcwak-768x429.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/159a9b31b861bcde780a6cbbfed13517-kix.iannqikdcwak-jpg.webp 1138w" width="1024" height="571" /></a> </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="【尊达兽】超强介绍！ 10 分钟了解民俗 [VTuber #Meguru Moroboshi]" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/3Jrzv0V_JsY?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> GAMABOOKS 旗下<a href="https://www.youtube.com/@meguru.gamabooks" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>书商 Vtuber Meguru Morohoshi</strong></a>是一位擅长民俗的 VTuber。这里提到的民俗学是一门通过揭示历史和民俗来探索各种日常事件、物体和概念的起源和意义的研究。</p><p>通过观看尊达兽和诸星巡的谈话视频系列，您可以清楚地理解这一点。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="【民间传说/解说】石头、剪刀、布乒乓球！大家仍然不知道剪刀石头布的历史……剪刀石头布的民间传说 [VTuber/#Meguru Moroboshi]" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/jR3YMmW_ksw?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="【比较文化/评论】烟草从哪里来，又是如何传播的？ [书店店员 VTuber #Meguru Moroboshi]" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/IK_8P3k-Ne8?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>每期节目都会确定一个主题，比如妖怪、香烟、公共浴室、小麦、红蓝等颜色，从民俗、当代研究、文化史的角度进行轻松的解说，同时展示大量的素材。 。有很多方面让你怀疑这是否是一个有效的主题，听完之后，你看待世界的分辨率将会大大提高。</p><p>她活泼的说话方式使人容易听懂，这也是她演讲的独特之处。看来她经常在城里散步，也经常旅行，在SNS上发布了很多照片。如果你也看看这个，你可以感受到诸星巡是如何看待世界的，通过学者的眼睛看世界是很有趣的。</p><p>我们还与各种文科VTuber和“ <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hHrjGYhXNlo" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Yuru Folklore Radio</a> ”合作。他似乎利用了自己高超的沟通能力，进行了实地考察，与各地的当地人交谈。</p><h2>日本历史/Kirako</h2><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/159a9b31b861bcde780a6cbbfed13517-kix.w6k8ex8n88f4-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/159a9b31b861bcde780a6cbbfed13517-kix.w6k8ex8n88f4-1024x572.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/159a9b31b861bcde780a6cbbfed13517-kix.w6k8ex8n88f4-1024x572.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/159a9b31b861bcde780a6cbbfed13517-kix.w6k8ex8n88f4-300x168.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/159a9