loads/2024/04/5dd01853c2c53cf1634953f7ec51cd03-kix.51s8ocefkyi-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/5dd01853c2c53cf1634953f7ec51cd03-kix.51s8ocefkyi-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/5dd01853c2c53cf1634953f7ec51cd03-kix.51s8ocefkyi-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/5dd01853c2c53cf1634953f7ec51cd03-kix.51s8ocefkyi-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/5dd01853c2c53cf1634953f7ec51cd03-kix.51s8ocefkyi-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/5dd01853c2c53cf1634953f7ec51cd03-kix.51s8ocefkyi-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a><br /> （从左上方，8月的两个人，两个雪，卢卡·库莫，地铁，阿里卡·纳加斯）</p><p>上周4月20日，出现了豪华艺术家，例如Sana Natori，Spring Saru -San，Koku -San和Kinu。这是最后一天被填充空间以及歌曲和音乐的粒子制作所淹没，但还有另一位歌手吸引了人们的关注。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/5dd01853c2c53cf1634953f7ec51cd03-kix.1hxp4zhfd9om-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/5dd01853c2c53cf1634953f7ec51cd03-kix.1hxp4zhfd9om-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/5dd01853c2c53cf1634953f7ec51cd03-kix.1hxp4zhfd9om-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/5dd01853c2c53cf1634953f7ec51cd03-kix.1hxp4zhfd9om-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/5dd01853c2c53cf1634953f7ec51cd03-kix.1hxp4zhfd9om-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/5dd01853c2c53cf1634953f7ec51cd03-kix.1hxp4zhfd9om-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/5dd01853c2c53cf1634953f7ec51cd03-kix.1hxp4zhfd9om-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p>她的名字叫<strong>猫</strong>。这是一位新的虚拟歌手，他在Meta =结舞台上首次亮相。</p><h2>以三首原创歌曲首次亮相！虚拟Akasaka Blitz中出现的新秀Vsinger“猫的sappense”是什么？</h2><p>唯一在表演者中没有名字或外表的秘密艺术家，由16位艺术家命名。那就是<strong>猫的味道</strong>。</p><p>看起来像是新秀虚拟歌手，没有任何警告出现，但实际上，提前准备了一点“气味”。在节日期间，许多参观Vrchat的Akasaka Blitz的人目睹了世界上的“猫”。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/5dd01853c2c53cf1634953f7ec51cd03-kix.w1gxcwz0vchs-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/5dd01853c2c53cf1634953f7ec51cd03-kix.w1gxcwz0vchs-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/5dd01853c2c53cf1634953f7ec51cd03-kix.w1gxcwz0vchs-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/5dd01853c2c53cf1634953f7ec51cd03-kix.w1gxcwz0vchs-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/5dd01853c2c53cf1634953f7ec51cd03-kix.w1gxcwz0vchs-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/5dd01853c2c53cf1634953f7ec51cd03-kix.w1gxcwz0vchs-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/5dd01853c2c53cf1634953f7ec51cd03-kix.w1gxcwz0vchs-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p> - 是的，这只猫是猫的味道。</p><p>猫的猫是最初花费的家猫的猫，但“更多的谈话”渴望到达了这颗星星，有一天是人类。他并不总是是一个人，通常他和这只猫一起在互联网世界中闲逛。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/5dd01853c2c53cf1634953f7ec51cd03-kix.odhqhxu84v0-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/5dd01853c2c53cf1634953f7ec51cd03-kix.odhqhxu84v0-1024x1024.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/5dd01853c2c53cf1634953f7ec51cd03-kix.odhqhxu84v0-1024x1024.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/5dd01853c2c53cf1634953f7ec51cd03-kix.odhqhxu84v0-300x300.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/5dd01853c2c53cf1634953f7ec51cd03-kix.odhqhxu84v0-150x150.webp 150w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/5dd01853c2c53cf1634953f7ec51cd03-kix.odhqhxu84v0-768x768.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/5dd01853c2c53cf1634953f7ec51cd03-kix.odhqhxu84v0-1536x1536.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/5dd01853c2c53cf1634953f7ec51cd03-kix.odhqhxu84v0-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="1024" /></a></p><p>在这个节日的首次亮相中，它变成了一只猫，该猫在场地外面围绕着，变成了一个具有可爱和尊严的人物，并出现在舞台上。</p><p>他以庄重的外表演唱了乔恩·亚基特（Jon-Yakitory）提供的歌曲“ <strong>Born</strong> ”，后者在“ Chaos Bugg”和“Feat。Ado”上工作，并亮起了Virtual Akasaka Blitz Red的场地。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/5dd01853c2c53cf1634953f7ec51cd03-kix.fznssziu5b49-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/5dd01853c2c53cf1634953f7ec51cd03-kix.fznssziu5b49-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/5dd01853c2c53cf1634953f7ec51cd03-kix.fznssziu5b49-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/5dd01853c2c53cf1634953f7ec51cd03-kix.fznssziu5b49-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/5dd01853c2c53cf1634953f7ec51cd03-kix.fznssziu5b49-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/5dd01853c2c53cf1634953f7ec51cd03-kix.fznssziu5b49-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/5dd01853c2c53cf1634953f7ec51cd03-kix.fznssziu5b49-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/5dd01853c2c53cf1634953f7ec51cd03-kix.ldfoftjaspi2-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/5dd01853c2c53cf1634953f7ec51cd03-kix.ldfoftjaspi2-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/5dd01853c2c53cf1634953f7ec51cd03-kix.ldfoftjaspi2-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/5dd01853c2c53cf1634953f7ec51cd03-kix.ldfoftjaspi2-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/5dd01853c2c53cf16349